  "texts": [
    "It enables devices to communicate with each other through the Internet (Sharma et al., 2020).",
    "The term IoT refers to the connection of everyday physical objects to the Internet, allowing for autonomous information sharing and task performance (Singh 2023; Qamar and Zardari 2023; Salama et al. 2023; Raja et al. 2023).",
    "Technological innovation has a significant impact on society today, both economically and socially.",
    "As a result, the use of agricultural technology and various innovations such as biotechnology, novel materials, photonics, big data, and the Internet of Things has increased.",
    "These advancements can be utilized to meet and sustain the demand (Worldometers 2017)."
